valinta__suomifi-tunnistaminen-roadmap: Suomi.fi e-Identification is a shared identification service for public administration e-services. It will make identification secure and easy. You can use the identification method of your preference.
valinta__toisten_maiden_tunnistautumista: Use the identification service of an other EU Member State
valinta__vaihtoehto__otsikko_valitse_maa: Select country in the common European identification scheme (eIDAS)
valinta__vaihtoehto__eIDAS_text: With <1>eIDAS identification</1>, you can use e-services provided by public administration in all EU countries across national borders.
valinta__palaa_tunnistajan_valintaan: Go back to method of identification
valinta__selain_ei_tue_tls1_2_p1: Your browser or end device needs updating
valinta__selain_ei_tue_tls1_2_p2: Your web browser or end device no longer adequately meets the data security requirements of strong electronic identification.
valinta__selain_ei_tue_tls1_2_p3: As a result, you will not be able to use the Suomi.fi identification with your old browser or device version after 5th June.
valinta__selain_ei_tue_tls1_2_p4: The data protection regulations of public administration are updated regularly, as there are data security risks involved with the use of old browsers and end devices.
